>fearn</i>). Modern use of this word as a given name dates from the 19th century, when it is also recorded occasionally as a boy's name in the United States. In some instances the given name may be a transferred use of the surname derived in the medieval period from the vocabulary word."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Angharad ferch Cynwrig Sais was born in 1200, in Ysceifiog, Flintshire, Wales, United Kingdom as the daughter of Hen Cynwrig Sais ap Ithel Fychan ap Growny. She had at least 1 daughter with Sir Rowling Oddyle."},"et":{"1200–":"1200–Surnud","1200–Female":"1200–Surnud","1270–Female":"1270–Surnud","1200–Male":"1200–Surnud","1230–1267":"1230–1267","1180–Male":"1180–Surnud","1267":"1267","1200":"1200","1230":"1230","1270":"1270","1180":"1180","Tre-fraith,Ysgeifiog,Flintshire,Wales":"Ysceifiog, Flintshire, Wales, United Kingdom","{Edwin}":"Edwin, Prantsuse Guajaana","Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shrewsbury, Shropshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1200–":"1200–Kuollut","1200–Female":"1200–Kuollut","1270–Female":"1270–Kuollut","1200–Male":"1200–Kuollut","1230–1267":"1230–1267","1180–Male":"1180–Kuollut","1267":"1267","1200":"1200","1230":"1230","1270":"1270","1180":"1180","Tre-fraith,Ysgeifiog,Flintshire,Wales":"Ysceifiog, Flintshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","{Edwin}":"Edwin, Ranskan Guayana","Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shrewsbury, Shropshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1200–":"1200–Décédée","1200–Female":"1200–Décédée","1270–Female":"1270–Décédée","1200–Male":"1200–Décédé","1230–1267":"1230–1267","1180–Male":"1180–Décédé","1267":"1267","1200":"1200","1230":"1230","1270":"1270","1180":"1180","Tre-fraith,Ysgeifiog,Flintshire,Wales":"Ysceifiog, Flintshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","{Edwin}":"Edwin, Guyane française","Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shrewsbury, Shropshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Angharad ferch Cynwrig Sais est née en 1200, à Ysceifiog, Flintsh